ðŸ“Œ 8. High-MRP Low-Discount Products

Identified products with:

MRP > 500

Discount < 10%

These represent premium items with high profit margins.

Useful for margin-focused promotions.


ðŸ“Œ 9. Highest Average Discount Categories

Top 5 categories with the highest average discount percentages were extracted.

Provides insights into:

