Customer-attracting categories

Potential areas of over-discounting


ðŸ“Œ 10. Price Per Gram Analysis

Identified products above 100g and calculated:

price_per_gram = discountedSellingPrice / weightInGms

Helps in:

Comparing product value across brands

Highlighting best-value products

Bulk purchase planning


